''AKA Restricted mode, Slave mode, Problem state''

In [[User Mode]], the [[CPU|Central Processing Unit]] will __not__ execute a large portion of its instruction set, responsible for things like direct memory access and other critical actions that are only supposed to be performed by the [[OS|Operating System]] and not any application software.